# Mobile Responsiveness Rules (Auto)

- Check that all UI components scale properly on:
  - Mobile (<480px), tablet (768px), and desktop (>1024px).
- Use fluid layouts, relative units (%, rem, vw/vh), and media queries.
- Suggest or apply improvements for:
  - Viewport configuration.
  - Touch target size.
  - Layout breakpoints.
- Run after editing HTML/CSS files.
